summary: Just Replacer for Adrianne Avenicci from Warmaiden's in Whiterun.
descriptionHtml:
[font=Comic Sans MS][color=#ffe599]     Hello guys :)
     This MOD is just replacer for Adrianne Avenicci from Warmaiden's in Whiterun.
     Her meshes and Textures are standalone. CBBE and UNP body only.

     Also I made Replacer for Ulfberth War_Bear's appearance.
     [/color][color=#ff0000]06,03,2016 Added Ulfberth only file.[/color]
[color=#ffe599]     (but Head mesh and Head parts only. So you can use any male body types)[/color]
[color=#ffe599]     You can choose it If you want ;P[/color]


     [color=#ff0000][size=5][u]Important Notes[/u][/size][/color]
[color=#ff0000][size=4]     This MOD is not support Wet and Cold MOD or something like that.
     If u use that, Adrianne will get Hair clipping with Hood from that MOD.
     But Plz dont ask me support for that. I dont.... Sorry.[/size][/color]

[color=#ffe599][img]http://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/110/images/73967-0-1457067609.png[/img][/color]

[/font][font=Comic Sans MS][color=#ff0000][size=5]Attention!![/size][/color][/font]
[font=Comic Sans MS][color=#ff0000]     Plz don't use console commands
     "coc whiterunwarmaidens"
     If you use that, you will get their face bug, So Plz.....[/color][/font]

[font=Comic Sans MS][color=#e69138][size=5]Notes[/size]
     If you use Warmaiden's interior overhaul mods,
     Plz adjustment load order like this

     Sean'sWhiterunOverhaul.esp     (Just Example. U know lol)
     Sean'sWarmaidens Overhaul.esp
     [u]MyWarmaidens.esp[/u]

     I mean Plz install this MOD after interior overhaul MODs.       

     [/color][color=#ff0000][size=4]If i make a mistakes, Plz don't be mad at me :P[/size][/color]

[color=#e69138][img]http://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/110/images/73967-0-1457071501.png[/img][/color]

[color=#980000][size=4]known issue[/size][/color]
[color=#980000]     One user said "When Adrianne at the grindstone,
     the iron sword that you should be shown is invisible"
     I checked about it, but i couldn't find that issue in my game ......(Please see my Image)
     but If you install this MOD, Please take care about it. Sorry
[img]http://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/110/images/73967-0-1457788781.jpg[/img]
[/color]
